'''流感基因组测序计划'''（{{lang-en|Influenza Genome Sequencing Project}}，缩写'''IGSP'''）是由[[美国|美国]][[國家衛生院_(美國)|国立卫生研究院]]（{{lang|en|National Institutes of Health}}，NIH）下辖的[[美國國家過敏和傳染病研究所|國家過敏和傳染病研究所]]（{{lang|en|National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases}}，NIAID）2004年发起的[[流感病毒|流感病毒]][[基因组|基因组]][[测序|测序]]计划，旨在帮助研究人员了解流感病毒是如何进化、传播和致病的。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Simonsen |first1=Lone |last2=Bernabe |first2=Gayle |last3=Lacourciere |first3=Karen |last4=Taylor |first4=Robert J. |last5=Giovanni |first5=Maria Y. |title=The NIAID Influenza Genome Sequencing Project |journal=National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases, NIH |date=2008 |pages=109–113 |doi=10.1007/978-1-59745-569-5_13}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.niaid.nih.gov/dmid/genomes/mscs/influenza.htm |title=Influenza Genome Sequencing Project |website=NIAID: Division of Microbiology & Infectious Diseases |publisher=National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases |accessdate=May 25, 2011 |archive-date=July 13, 2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070713094554/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/dmid/genomes/mscs/influenza.htm }}</ref>

